minute call costs will be the same state to state. take note of the recharge options and prices in the state that you originally bought your sim, because as you move to other areas in india, the local recharge options vary and will not apply to you (they'll only apply to sim's bought in that state). for example, if you bought your sim in goa and to get rs100 talk time credited to your account, you actually paid rs120 (rs100 talk time + rs20 local taxes), but then travelled to another state where they had a promotion where rs100 talk 